Modification statement:
The original GF180MCU 3.3V primitive device models (nmos_3p3, pmos_3p3) are
distributed as .subckt wrappers around binned, corner-based, statistically-
parameterised BSIM4 cards. In this derived work those models were COLLAPSED
into flat BSIM4 (level 54) .model cards:
  - corner: typical (t)
  - statistics / mismatch: disabled (global and mismatch = 0)
  - fit bin: L in [0.28, 0.5] um, W in [0.5, 1.2] um (device bin 4)
  - binning length/width correction terms retained (binunit=2)
See README.md for validation results and usage limitations.

